582
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,300
Grandmother, is everything okay?

583
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,650
Yes. Yes. it is.

584
00:36:01,820 --> 00:36:02,940
Good to see you guys.

585
00:36:03,860 --> 00:36:04,730
Have a seat, Grandmother.

586
00:36:08,170 --> 00:36:08,900
Old Madam,

587
00:36:10,050 --> 00:36:10,940
I'm sorry you had to go through that.

588
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,250
My sweet Yansheng and Tianlei,

589
00:36:13,570 --> 00:36:15,340
